{"tid":2512750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦附近均益法團換屆 親建制又輸 包圍大台起閧","createTime":"2021-05-02T03:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T05:22:07.000Z","uid":189046,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a43b3766d43ed48823fd316a56c2ca7d6c340c8","tid":2512750,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdcsRDdrkiBocP3wkVX7LP1MwwwUPaDzhVPsuEoXJacey?filename=8Lr3e5u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Lr3e5u.png&h=59ba293f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/videos/304613294380638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fvideos%2F304613294380638&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=c333c995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/videos/304613294380638</a><br />\n位於中聯辦附近、樓齡超過 40 年的西環均益大廈二期，昨（1 日）晚舉行法團換屆選舉。現屆開明派法團 3 年前「踢走」連任逾 20 年的親建制法團，親建制派今屆組 11 人名單捲土重來。點票程序今 ( 2 日) 晨完成，由開明派居民籌組的 6 人名單全數當選，繼續保留在業主立案法團的話事權，親建制名單則取得另外 5 席。大會進行期間兩派居民多番口角，衝突不斷，親建制一方多次包圍協調會議的法團秘書，質疑主持人選、不滿開明派欲臨時籌組 11 人名單等，並指傳媒無權在場，一度指罵驅趕記者出場，多次聲言報警。<br />\n<br />\n選法團程序甫開始即爆衝突<br />\n<br />\n均益二期過去一直被視為民建聯票倉（見另稿），亦是民建聯西營盤辦事處所在地。該廈親建制業主立案法團連任逾 23 年，直至 2018 年才由開明派街坊勝出。曾被懷疑參與種票的前副主席倪法昇今屆「捲土重來」，籌組 11 人名單欲重掌法團。<br />\n<br />\n由於街坊過去以為法團名單中，商鋪代表和住戶代表需分別為 5 人和 6 人，故由現屆開明派委員牽頭的名單只有 6 人，沒有商鋪代表。及至在場的民政處代表解釋，根據條例法團只需 9 人出選已足夠，亦沒有成員代表限制，惟居民最後仍將法團人數議決為 11 人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E8%A5%BF%E7%92%B0%E5%9D%87%E7%9B%8A%E4%BA%8C%E6%9C%9F%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%98%E6%8F%9B%E5%B1%86-%E9%96%8B%E6%98%8E%E6%B4%BE-6-%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%85%A8%E6%95%B8%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8-%E8%A6%AA%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E8%B6%95%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%259D%2587%25E7%259B%258A%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%2598%25E6%258F%259B%25E5%25B1%2586-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%25B4%25BE-6-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25B6%2595%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=dd5dc565\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%259D%2587%25E7%259B%258A%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%2598%25E6%258F%259B%25E5%25B1%2586-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%25B4%25BE-6-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25B6%2595%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F&h=aee0f05c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E8%A5%BF%E7%92%B0%E5%9D%87%E7%9B%8A%E4%BA%8C%E6%9C%9F%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%98%E6%8F%9B%E5%B1%86-%E9%96%8B%E6%98%8E%E6%B4%BE-6-%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%85%A8%E6%95%B8%E7%95%B6%E9%81%B8-%E8%A6%AA%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E8%B6%95%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4/</a>"},{"pid":"7bff1643fc34324c2f0a222edd5efaf294621840","tid":2512750,"uid":18649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:55:08.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d67f20f3bb0a56c8227753b94bbeb9a4563639","tid":2512750,"uid":287461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T03:59: